{"tid":2342993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"普京將接種俄制疫苗證安全有效 習近平表示 ... ...","createTime":"2020-12-27T14:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T14:35:06.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f30bea5de5df228baeee7d5b1377e142d7a254d","tid":2342993,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:25:27.000Z","msg":"普京將接種俄羅斯新冠疫苗<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯克里姆林宮表示，總統普京已決定接種由本國研發的新型冠狀病毒疫苗「衛星V」，正等候完成手續。68歲的普京早前表明，俄羅斯疫苗有效安全，他沒有理由不接種。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯今個月初啟動「衛星V」疫苗的自願接種計劃，先在莫斯科推行，市長索比亞寧說，60歲以上人士星期一起可預約注射疫苗。自俄羅斯爆發疫情以來，普京的工作都保持社交距離，主要透過網上和有限度訪問舉行會議。他8月時透露，女兒參加了疫苗臨床試驗，事後感覺良好。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2372399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2372399&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=21a6420c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2372399</a>"},{"pid":"8180f97d05b7aaa07babc99997994dd124805730","tid":2342993,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"習近平表示輝瑞的接種後同樣良好"},{"pid":"59c3fe0a87becc40553f9d395d3aa32798fa6c77","tid":2342993,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:26:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://j.gifs.com/lxB0Qj.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FlxB0Qj.gif&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=908abed0\" target=\"_blank\">https://j.gifs.com/lxB0Qj.gif</a>"},{"pid":"5c308169a593fd5a6ab76da8b5f60c09d9f38e40","tid":2342993,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CiKBSR1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCiKBSR1.gif&h=00e78384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打完變身"},{"pid":"2359d574fac53d4f5d4c76c3d66ead12adc564a2","tid":2342993,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike